---
import Container from "@/components/Container";
import { Button } from "@/components/ui/button";
---

<section class="min-h-[40rem] flex items-center justify-center">
  <Container
    className="w-fit relative flex flex-col laptop:flex-row justify-center items-center gap-8"
  >
    <img
      src="/images/about-us/about-us-2.webp"
      alt="Thagai Healthcare Services - Showcasing our comprehensive care solutions"
      class="w-[20rem] tablet:w-[32rem] laptop:-translate-x-56 desktop:w-[41.875rem] desktop:-translate-x-67"
      width={670}
    />

    <div
      class="laptop:absolute w-full tablet:w-[35.625rem] flex flex-col items-center gap-[2.0625rem] laptop:translate-x-50 desktop:translate-y-14 desktop:translate-x-67"
    >
      <h2
        class="uppercase font-bold text-[2rem] tablet:text-[2.5rem] text-primary laptop:translate-x-10 desktop:translate-x-0"
      >
        What is Thagai?
      </h2>

      <div
        class="flex flex-col gap-[0.9375rem] bg-custom-purple p-[1.875rem] w-full"
      >
        <p
          class="text-justify text-primary font-normal text-normal tablet:text-[1.25rem]"
        >
          At Thagai, we are more than just a care service providerâ€”we are a
          compassion-driven initiative committed to making quality care
          accessible and affordable for all. Founded by a team of young minds,
          Thagai was born from a deep understanding of the challenges working
          individuals face in finding reliable and affordable care. Our mission
          is to bridge this gap with safe, compassionate, and high-quality
          services tailored to the diverse needs of our clients.
        </p>
        <a href="/services">
          <Button
            className="uppercase text-justify text-white w-full max-w-[16.4375rem] h-[3.6875rem] cursor-pointer"
            >Explore Our Services</Button
          >
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Container>
</section>
